article.description: — Antonio TJ Madlock had a season-high 20 points plus 10 rebounds as South Carolina State got past Charleston Southern 75-65 on Tuesday.
article.headline: Madlock carries SC State over Charleston Southern 75-65
article.linkText: Madlock carries SC State over Charleston Southern 75-65
article.story: CHARLESTON, S.C. -- — Antonio TJ Madlock had a season-high 20 points plus 10 rebounds as South Carolina State got past Charleston Southern 75-65 on Tuesday. Cameron Jones had 17 points and eight rebounds for South Carolina State (7-8), which won its fourth consecutive game. Deaquan Williams added 12 points. Edward Oliver-Hampton had seven rebounds. Charleston Southern scored 21 points in the second half, a season low for the team. Claudell Harris Jr. had 18 points for the Buccaneers (3-9). Kalib Clinton added 14 points. Taje' Kelly had 12 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
